                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.05/156: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-07-27T12:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 27, 1929—noon</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>251. Your 626, July 25, 11 a.m. The draft note quoted in your telegram is
                    acceptable to the Department.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
